            <span id=3D"pu374"></span>

                        <div class=3D"toc_wrapper"><div class=3D"toc_title"=
>Table of Contents</div><ul id=3D"toc" style=3D""><li><a href=3D"https://ww=
w.supermagnete.de/eng/magnetism/Gauss-and-tesla#what-do-the-units-gauss-and=
-tesla-represent">What do the units gauss and tesla represent?</a></li><li>=
<a href=3D"https://www.supermagnete.de/eng/magnetism/Gauss-and-tesla#the-na=
mes-behind-the-units-of-gauss-and-tesla">The names behind the units of gaus=
s and tesla</a><ul><li><a href=3D"https://www.supermagnete.de/eng/magnetism=
/Gauss-and-tesla#information-about-jcf-gauss">Information about J.C.F.
Gauss</a></li><li><a href=3D"https://www.supermagnete.de/eng/magnetism/Gaus=
s-and-tesla#information-about-nikola-tesla">Information about Nikola Tesla<=
/a></li></ul></li></ul></div>
                  </div>
  </div>
 =20
